                <mxCell id="note_switch_only" value="&lt;b&gt;After step ⑤ (FlowMod install):&lt;/b&gt;  All subsequent packets in both directions (Client ↔ WS and WS ↔ MongoDB) are forwarded entirely by the OVS switch — the SDN controller is NOT involved.  Rules expire after idle_timeout (30 s default) or hard_timeout (120 s default), triggering a new Packet-In for the next connection." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;fontColor=#333333;fontSize=12;dashed=1;align=left;spacingLeft=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
